        <title>Menu not working when deploy</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[andrius.zibaitis96]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I fixed this. Problem is with subdomain.<br>
If you deploy this with subdomain and you don’t have SSL sertificate, your website not loading links…</p>
<p>So I change it:</p>
<p>source: {<br>
url: “wp.yourdomain.is”,<br>
homepage: “/home-page/”,</p>
<p>source: {<br>
url: “yourdomain.is/wp/”,<br>
homepage: “/home-page/”,</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/menu-not-working-when-deploy/4569/6">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
